    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392010/extras/900dcb6566c884924b11fefd3b54a103.avif?t=1769858473\" width=548 height=160 /></span><br><br><strong>Heat Division: Rescue Team</strong> is an intense 2D systemic speedrunning platformer. Take control of one of the four distinct members of the Rescue Team and make your way through several urban environments, as seen through the lens of an expressive and colorful pixel art, and safely rescue the civilians trapped within natural and man-made disasters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392010/extras/1b854bf6eb2b7c4a4217bd586cbbc643.avif?t=1769858473\" width=546 height=147 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Systemic speedrun platformer with warm Cyberfunk-inspired visuals seen through grungy but cartoonish pixel-art.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4 playable firefighters with unique abilities. Rescue civilians from burning buildings, natural/artificial disasters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Find the fastest way to complete each mission, using tools provided: ladders, water buckets, axes to destroy objects blocking the way, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Designed to support high refresh rates (above 60hz)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392010/extras/3e349229399bbd7ff1aee903d1ee904b.avif?t=1769858473\" width=549 height=159 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2392010/extras/c60ab068734aa52f97cb456ab3139e36.avif?t=1769858473\